3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) - The paper proposes a method for improving the performance of automated algorithms in fetal ultrasound screening, which is an application of artificial intelligence. 
4. cs.Medical Imaging - The paper specifically focuses on improving ultrasound scan plane detection, which is a subfield of medical imaging.
